Ask HN: What's important in a deep learning model poster?
text:
Hi all,

For a university project, my group was tasked with building and training a deep learning model for certain image classification problems. We need to present a poster of our model and results, and I was wondering which metrics are important, and how to present them? (other than the obvious train/test accuracy and confusion matrix)

Any creative ideas on how to visualize the results?

Thanks!
